OL,3,CSchool suspensions hit record high of
OL,4,C247,400 last autumn term, study says
OL,6,FThere was a record high of a quarter
OL,7,Fof a million suspensions from school
OL,8,Fin last year's autumn term, affecting
OL,9,F135,000 pupils, according to new data.
OL,11,FAn analysis of Department for
OL,12,FEducation data by the Centre for
OL,13,FSocial Justice found that 3,051 young
OL,14,Fpeople were permanently excluded over
OL,15,Fthe 2021/22 academic year, with rates
OL,16,Fnearly back to pre-pandemic heights.
